name: $itemSequence
desc: Returns: The sequence number of the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error occurs outside of the item structure.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The sequence number of the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error occurs outside of the item structure.

name: $detailSequence
desc: Returns: The sequence number of the detail within the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error occurs outside of the item structure.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The sequence number of the detail within the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error occurs outside of the item structure.

name: $subDetailSequence
desc: Returns: The sequence number of the sub-detail within the detail within the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error occurs outside of the item structure.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The sequence number of the sub-detail within the detail within the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error occurs outside of the item structure.

name: $code
desc: Returns: An error code, from a specified code system, which details why the claim could not be adjudicated.
